tiful’ and then, from the 16th century, ‘light in colouring’)."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"When Blanche de Beaufort was born in 1051, in Beaufort-Blavincourt, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, France, her father, Gaucher de Beaufort, was 26 and her mother, Marie de Habarcq, was 15. She married Wallérand D'AVESNES-DE GAND. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. She died in 1107, in Avesnes-sur-Helpe, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France, at the age of 56."},"et":{"1051–1107":"1051–1107","1055–1109":"1055–1109","1057–1115":"1057–1115","1034–1094":"1034–1094","1065–1138":"1065–1138","1025–1089":"1025–1089","1036–1087":"1036–1087","1055":"1055","1065":"1065","1087":"1087","1051":"1051","1094":"1094","1107":"1107","1138":"1138","1115":"1115","1036":"1036","1025":"1025","1057":"1057","1089":"1089","1034":"1034","1109":"1109","Avesnes-le-Comte, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, France":"Avesnes-le-Comte, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, Prantsusmaa","Beaufort-Blavincourt, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, França":"Beaufort-Blavincourt, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, Prantsusmaa","Avesnes, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France":"Avesnes, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, Prantsusmaa","Avesnes-sur-Helpe, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, França":"Avesnes-sur-Helpe, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, Prantsusmaa","Beaufort-Blavincourt, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, França":"Beaufort-Blavincourt, Pas-de-Calais, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1051–1107":"1051–1107","1055–1109":"1055–1109","1057–1115":"1057–1115","1034–1094":"1034–1094","1065–1138":"1065–1138","1025–1089":"1025–1089","1036–1087":"1036–1087","1055":"1055","1065":"1065","1087":"1087","1051":"1051","1094":"1094","1107":"1107","1138":"1138","1115":"1115","1036":"1036","1025":"1025","1057":"1057","1089":"1089","1034":"1034","1109":"1109","Avesnes-le-Comte, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, France":"Avesnes-le-Comte, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, Ranska","Beaufort-Blavincourt, Pas-de-Calais, Hauts-de-France, Fran